{
  "texts": [
    "QiZhenGPT-eval 53 focuses on drug indication evaluation, tasking LLMs with identifying diseases for which a given drug is suitable.",
    "However, single-task datasets are overly restrictive in evaluation dimensions and may not reflect other medical competencies.",
    "Consequently, various integrated datasets have been gradually proposed.",
    "CBLUE (Zhang et al, 2022) is an evaluation dataset for Chinese medical language understanding, presenting five medical tasks using authentic medical data.",
    "It assesses LLMs in medical text information extraction and medical Q&A."
  ]
}